step3:Run makeall in terminal after entering into the folder of Mutex.
step4:Output files will be created.
       send      receiver
step5:Run the ./send output file one terminal and ./receiver output file in another terminals.
step6:Once you enter the data in the sender file terminal, it will be displayed in the receiver file.